12 Initiative: Provides funding for one Auditor III position, 2 Field Investigator Supervisor
13 positions, 4 Auditor II positions and 12 OCP Compliance Inspector positions and
14 associated All Other costs.
15 GENERAL FUND 2025-26 2026-27
16 POSITIONS - LEGISLATIVE COUNT 19.000 19.000
